			<h2>Expert technology guidance for growing businesses</h2>
<p>Not every business needs a full-time CTO, but every business making technology decisions deserves expert guidance. Our Fractional CTO service gives you access to senior technology leadership exactly when you need it, without the commitment of a full-time hire.</p>

<p>We start with honesty. If we can't help you, we'll tell you straight away. No bluffing, no pretending, no wasted time. When we can help, we offer a clear pathway from initial conversation through to delivered software.</p>

<h3>What a fractional CTO actually does for you</h3>

<p>A fractional CTO sits alongside your leadership and makes the technology calls a CTO would make – without being on your payroll five days a week. In practice that means deciding what to build next and what to leave alone, reviewing the work your team or suppliers are doing and telling you straight when something’s off, sense-checking quotes and contracts before you sign, helping you assess technical hires, and owning the roadmap so your business plan and what actually gets built line up.</p>

<p>The point isn’t hours of CTO time for the sake of it. The point is that you make the next twelve months of technology decisions with senior input, instead of guessing.</p>

